      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in impeccable condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail. The exterior maintains its original showroom luster, complemented by an interior that exhibits no discernible signs of wear. Beyond its aesthetic perfection, all mechanical systems have been comprehensively vetted to ensure peak performance and absolute reliability. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade asset that satisfies the most exacting standards of quality and provenance. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this exemplary specimen.",
      "price": 43500.0,
